"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-10-afghan-refugee-athlete-disqualified-olympic-breakdancing-event-21397650\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ManizhaTalash, a member of the refugee Olympic team at theParisGames, was controversially disqualified from the breakdancing event.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Talash displayed the words 'Free Afghan Women' on her cape during her routine in the competition's pre-qualifiers on Friday.\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 257, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The dancer, who lives in Spain, wore a light blue cape that had the phrase written on it with large white letters during her pre-qualifier loss to India Sardjoe of Netherlands.\", \"from\": 259, \"to\": 435, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 284, \"end\": 289, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.9772002756456739, \"rank\": 0.019469396748620874, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}, {\"begin\": 406, \"end\": 411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.976820916651834, \"rank\": 0.014550042106365086, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 423, \"end\": 434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999071780413878, \"rank\": 6.531916469435252e-05, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Political slogans and statements are banned on the field of play and on podiums at theOlympicsand breaking's governing body later said the 21-year-old had been disqualified.\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 610, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Talashwas 'disqualified for displaying a political slogan on her attire,' World Dance